{"tid":1870112,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[和理非注意] 「突襲」賽狗圍捕新招","createTime":"2020-02-08T15:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T17:55:18.000Z","uid":36073,"like":182,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"169d12ac8a1b4baec41933cd5ded664d9cefe701","tid":1870112,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"由新年開始，狗開始有習性會突然向前衝去咬人，吠都唔吠就等你走唔到<br />\n<br />\n第一次見到呢招係粉嶺雍盛苑，狗官鳩up 吓野突然嗌「Go! Go! Go!」<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/AggressiveFoolhardyGalah-mobile.mp4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FAggressiveFoolhardyGalah-mobile.mp4&h=bcc4e94d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年初二 23:59 之前一粒TG 都冇放過，班狗又用新策略對付一群跑唔郁嘅和理非，連的士都dup到應一應<br />\n再加便衣接應，已經捉到實<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/GraveScholarlyHoverfly-mobile.mp4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FGraveScholarlyHoverfly-mobile.mp4&h=daaed259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位鍾意食花生嘅，一係就狗照衝都唔好跑，賽狗你未必跑得羸，你越跑佢就越想咬你<br />\n一係就狗衝之前，預先行定走，撚狗都唔好撚到醉晒<br />\n<br />\nBe Water<br />\n<br />\n（想重播，可以上一頁再click返入嚟）"},{"pid":"de793f67dcdb91ed6f039c31368f04d9ad9fc66a","tid":1870112,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:09:46.000Z","msg":"puhs"},{"pid":"357c834bca65265d560127e07d42428f8e188212","tid":1870112,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"死黑警 報應報應"},{"pid":"0c815c3fc5bc1ff722738885c0656304f1d1ffcf","tid":1870112,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:17:07.000Z","msg":"psuh"},{"pid":"e984fb6fec9e470715b80a706b8e106c62de3f0f","tid":1870112,"uid":36073,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:18:43.000Z","msg":"加片，請由0:00開始睇<br />\n<br />\n旺角<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6g8r5WmnyJM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6g8r5WmnyJM&d=CEXeqV